  "body": "### Description\nWhen a user fails to upgrade prior to a fork, they may import blocks after the fork epoch that are from the old milestone. After Teku is updated, it then fails to start because of those blocks.  Teku should delete the invalid blocks and resume syncing from either the latest finalized state or the last valid block.",
